ga:EWA76_MG69_Description_de a crm:E33_Linguistic_Object ;
    crm:P129_is_about ga:EWA76_MG69 ;
    crm:P190_has_symbolic_content "Im alten Teil des Basars von Almar sind die zur Strasse offenen dukanha (Läden) noch traditionell aus Lehm erstellt. Bastmatten schützen vor der starken Sonneneinstrahlung. Im Vordergrund sitzt ein Lastenträger in typisch gepolsterter und zerschlissener Arbeitskleidung im Schatten einer Föhre auf der Strasse. Das Seil auf seinem Rücken schlingt er um die Last und führt es über seine ebenfalls gepolsterte Stirne, wenn er stark nach vorn gebeugt bis zu 100 kg trägt."@de ;
    crm:P2_has_type ga:Image_Description_Type .

ga:EWA76_MG69_Description_de_Confidence a crm:E54_Dimension ;
    crm:P2_has_type ga:Confidence ;
    crm:P90_has_value 1.0 ;
    crm:P91_has_unit ga:Probability_Unit .

ga:EWA76_MG69_Description_en a crm:E33_Linguistic_Object ;
    crm:P129_is_about ga:EWA76_MG69 ;
    crm:P190_has_symbolic_content "In the old part of the Almar bazaar, the dukanha (shops) which are open to the street are still traditionally made of clay. Bast mats protect against the strong sunlight. In the foreground, a porter in typical padded and tattered working clothes sits in the shade of a pine tree on the street. He wraps the rope on his back around the load and guides it over his forehead, which is also padded, when he is leaning forward carrying a load of up to 100 kg.",
        "In the old part of the Almar bazaar, the dukanha (shops) which are open to the street are still traditionally made of clay. Bast mats protect against the strong sunlight. In the foreground, a porter in typical padded and tattered working clothes sits in the shade of a pine tree on the street. He wraps the rope on his back around the load and guides it over his forehead, which is also padded, when he is leaning forward carrying a load of up to 100 kg."@en ;
    crm:P2_has_type ga:Image_Description_Type .

ga:EWA76_MG69_Description_en_Confidence a crm:E54_Dimension ;
    crm:P2_has_type ga:Confidence ;
    crm:P90_has_value 1.0 ;
    crm:P91_has_unit ga:Probability_Unit .

ga:EWA76_MG69_Description_pl a crm:E33_Linguistic_Object ;
    crm:P129_is_about ga:EWA76_MG69 ;
    crm:P190_has_symbolic_content "W starej części bazaru Almar dukanha (sklepy) otwarte na ulicę są nadal tradycyjnie wykonane z gliny. Maty łykowe chronią przed silnym nasłonecznieniem. Na pierwszym planie tragarz w typowym wyściełanym i podartym ubraniu roboczym siedzi w cieniu sosny na ulicy. Owija linę na plecach wokół ładunku i prowadzi ją po czole, które jest również wyściełane, gdy pochyla się do przodu i dźwiga do 100 kg."@pl ;
    crm:P2_has_type ga:Image_Description_Type .

ga:EWA76_MG69_Description_pl_Confidence a crm:E54_Dimension ;
    crm:P2_has_type ga:Confidence ;
    crm:P90_has_value 1.0 ;
    crm:P91_has_unit ga:Probability_Unit .

