    crm:P129_is_about ga:EWA76_MG89 ;
    crm:P190_has_symbolic_content "On the edge of a partially flooded street, traders exhibited their wares on market day. The offer ranges from almonds in icing to shoes and shovel handles. An eye-catcher are the painted chests, wall stands, lamp stands and a cradle."@en ;
    crm:P2_has_type ga:Image_Description_Type .

